songs.title: Superstar (the Simpsons song)
songs.lyrics:
[Lisa Simpson]:
I used to think that I was stupid
Worthless weak and wrong
A mockingbird without a song
I was small inside
Left and ride
On a one-way train to be Milhouse's bride

[Milhouse Van Houten]:
End this song, end it right here!

I love NPR and jazz guitars
And may design a solar car
That's right
I'm Lisa Simpson superstar

[Lady Gaga]:
You've got a great big heart
That's at the top of the chart

[Both]:
Lisa Simpson
Lisa Simpson
Lisa Simpson superstar

Lisa Simpson
Lisa Simpson
Lisa Simpson superstar

[Lady Gaga]:
You're a superstar
